                    <h2>History of Mobile at ForeTees</h2>

                    <p>ForeTees has been adding mobile support ever since Apple introduced the first iPhone. &nbsp;The following 
                        timeline provides a summary of our progress to date. </p>

                    <ul>
                        <li>2007 - Purchased an iPhone the first day they went on sale and began testing our software.</li>
                        <li>2009 - Introduced ForeTees Mobile, a separate mobile ForeTees site for tee times.</li>
                        <li>2012 - Responsive Web Design (RWD) technology introduced to industry. &nbsp;ForeTees begins transforming entire product line to RWD.</li>
                        <li>2014 - ForeTees updates all of our member-facing software to Responsive Web Design to automatically support all mobile devices without the need of a separate mobile site.</li>
                        <li>2015 - ForeTees introduces the industry's first Mobile App designed exclusively for private clubs using ForeTees.</li>
                    </ul>

                    <h2>Our Commitment to You</h2>

                    <p>ForeTees was the first website/reservation provider in the industry to provide a mobile site for reservations. &nbsp;We were the first, and still the only, provider to offer all 
                        member-facing solutions in Responsive Web Design. &nbsp;And, we are the first to offer an App specifically designed for private clubs with ForeTees. &nbsp;<strong>We are the leader in mobile solutions for private clubs!</strong></p>

                    <p>The mobile technologies are changing and advancing at a very fast pace. &nbsp;ForeTees will continue to monitor these technologies and embrace those that will benefit our customers. &nbsp;We 
                        already have additional app features under development, with plans to introduce mobile solutions not seen in this industry before. &nbsp;We will continue to provide you with the tools you need 
                        to <strong>retain your membership, attract new members, and generate more revenue!</strong></p>

