                <article>
                    <header><h1>New Features</h1></header>

                    <h2>Course=ALL option on Old Tee Sheets (Golf)</h2>
                    <p>If your club utilizes our golf system and you have multiple courses, you will now be allowed to view all courses when accessing the past tee sheets. &nbsp;On this page
                        you will now see an -ALL- entry in the course selection list. Selecting this option will list the existing tee times for all courses.</p>

                    <h2>Send Push Notifications from ForeTees</h2>
                    <p>If you have the ClubCentral App, you can now send Push Notifications to your members directly from the Tee Sheet or Courts, or by using the new Send Push feature under Tools.</p>
                    <p>A new item labeled <strong>'Send Push Notification' has been added to the Control Panel</strong> on the tee sheet/court page. Selecting this item will open a page that is similar to the Send Email 
                        page. &nbsp;All members that are on the tee sheet or court, and have the app on at least one mobile device, will appear in the member list. &nbsp;All you need to do is enter a 
                        brief message and hit Send. &nbsp;The message will appear on the members' app immediately.</p>
                    <p>A new menu item also labeled <strong>'Send Push Notification' has been added to the Tools tab</strong> in the proshop Navigation. Selecting this menu item will open the same page as described above, 
                        though there will not be any pre-selected members. &nbsp;You will be allowed to select the recipients (members that have the app), enter a brief message, and then send it.</p>

                    <h2>Quickly and Easily Setup Members for the App from ForeTees</h2>
                    <p>Also if you have the ClubCentral App, you can quickly assist your members in getting setup with the ClubCentral App by using the new App Setup feature under Tools.</p>
                    <p>A new item labeled <strong>'ClubCentral App Setup' has been added to the Tools tab</strong>. &nbsp;Selecting this item will open a page that will allow you to select a member by name and then 
                        generate credentials for that member to login to the App once its installed on their mobile device. &nbsp;This is the only time they will need to login on that device, so there is no need for 
                        the member to record or memorize these credentials.</p>
                    <p>This feature will be especially helpful when a member walks into your shop, or when your club hosts an 'Appy Hour', or other event, to assist members in getting setup with the ClubCentral App. &nbsp;<strong>Please 
                            note we have created a special limited proshop login for staff that do not currently have proshop access</strong>.</p>
                    <p>Contact our sales team or support staff if you would like to know how to use this login.</p>
                </article>

